      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Josué Forte</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:105px;\"><a href=\"/File:Josueforte.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/90/Josueforte.jpg\" width=\"103\" height=\"192\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Josueforte.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Josué Forte <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Josué Forte</b>,<br />\na Brazilian computer scientist, computer chess programmer and author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine <a href=\"/Matheus\" title=\"Matheus\">Matheus</a>, \nwhich already had its tournament debut at <a href=\"/Don_Beal\" title=\"Don Beal\">Don Beal's</a> <a href=\"/UPCCC_1994\" title=\"UPCCC 1994\">Uniform-Platform CCC 1994</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nand was first published as <a href=\"/Category:WinBoard\" title=\"Category:WinBoard\">WinBoard engine</a> in 2002 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2002\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2002</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2003\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2003</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2004\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josu%C3%A9_Forte&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2002\">2002</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josu%C3%A9_Forte&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2002\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=38017\">Matheus 1.4 (Release: World Cup 2002 Champion!!)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, July 02, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=38268\">C/C++ compilers and its influence on the chess engine speed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, July 23, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=38959\">To: Leo Dijksman (Information about your next tornament)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 11, 2002</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2003\">2003</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josu%C3%A9_Forte&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2003\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=41366\">Assembly language for PC (Off topic)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 21, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Assembly\" title=\"Assembly\">Assembly</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=42991\">When can a game be declared as a draw?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 15, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Draw_Evaluation\" title=\"Draw Evaluation\">Draw Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=44182\">Porting an engine to Linux</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 18, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004\">2004</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josu%C3%A9_Forte&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2004\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=354615\">Matheus-2.3 released - With UCI support</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 14, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47383\">Need help: End Game Table Base and BitBase</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 24, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Bitbases\" title=\"Endgame Bitbases\">Endgame Bitbases</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josu%C3%A9_Forte&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=2374\">How to implement the UCI command \"currline\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 24, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=2436\">Arena and UCI commands</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 30, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=3405#p17152\">Re: Mate scores in the hash table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 04, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Score#MateScores\" title=\"Score\">Mate Scores</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josu%C3%A9_Forte&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20040804201711/http://www.matheuschess.hpg.ig.com.br/index.htm\">Matheus Chess HomePage</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20121209201403/http://wbec-ridderkerk.nl/html/details1/Matheus.html\">Matheus</a> from <a href=\"/WBEC\" title=\"WBEC\">WBEC Ridderkerk</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josu%C3%A9_Forte&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=3405#p17152\">Re: Mate scores in the hash table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Josué Forte</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 04, 2005</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Larry_Kaufman\" title=\"Larry Kaufman\">Larry Kaufman</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>1994 Uniform Platform Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Reports\" title=\"Computer Chess Reports\">Computer Chess Reports</a>, Vol. 5, No. 1, pp. 8</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20121209201403/http://wbec-ridderkerk.nl/html/details1/Matheus.html\">Matheus</a> from <a href=\"/WBEC\" title=\"WBEC\">WBEC Ridderkerk</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301125932\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 73/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 146/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7921-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301125932 and revision id 25237\n -->\n"
